These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
City: marseilles, nizza, boston, edinburgh
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, may, october
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person traveling to boston and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| City           | nizza | marseilles | boston   | edinburgh     |
| Birthday   | april    | may         | november | october         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

