.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, hedgehog, chinchilla
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, electrician, librarian, firefighter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the german is between the librarian and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the firefighter is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the fan of disco is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the electrician is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the firefighter##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the firefighter##1
10. the accountant is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the electrician##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the owner of the frog is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Pet      | chinchilla    | frog       | hedgehog   | guinea-pig |
| Job         | accountant     | librarian   | firefighter    | electrician  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel | thriller   | western     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       | electronic | folk        |
| Nationality   | pakistani | malaysian   | german     | canadian    |
| Transport     | bus       | ship        | train      | bike        |

