The people have 4 different hobbies: rosed-games, collecting, gardening, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, designer, scientist, software-developer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: american, french, malaysian, russian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, amaryllis, begonia
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the malaysian##2
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the designer##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the american##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growsrose is between the scientist and the person who's hobby is rosed-games##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is rosed-games is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
12. the software-developer is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the person playing scrabble is the person playing scrabble##1
14. the person who's hobby is gardening is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |     4     |
